title: Andrew Luck and NFL Predictions

description:
Colin discusses people bashing Andrew Luck’s early retirement, Aaron Rodgers comments on Luck, and more NFL predictions. Guests include Rob Parker, Bucky Brooks, T. J. Houshmandzadeh, and Vinny Bonsignore.
